Package: retractionpollution
Type: Package
Title: Trace Citation Pollution from Retracted and Concerning Scientific Papers
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Trace how retracted articles and expressions of concern continue to
    influence the scientific literature through citation descendants. Uses
    Retraction Watch seed records and OpenCitations for DOI-based citation
    lookup, and can optionally use OpenAlex for work resolution, recursive
    citation expansion, and metadata. Headline analysis exports a depth-2
    network, records validation checks for crawl completeness, provenance, and
    generated artifacts, and builds a fully reproducible manuscript whose
    numbers and figures are all generated from the study database.
